author: Truelikegiroux
body: Definitely not small! But I’m mostly thinking of revenue in the billions. F500s and tech companies just don’t care about travel, especially consulting companies who expense everything to clients. I have a bunch of friends in Accenture, Cognizant, and KPMG that have been flying and traveling for months
